label: HomeActivity
text: Get an idea of the yarn count of a fabric based on its yarn diameter or the other way around an estimation of the yarn diameter based on the fabrics’ yarn count. YARN DIAMETER & COUNT CALCULATOR Gives an indication of how dense or heavy a given fabric is thus allowing you to compare it to other fabrics and decide if it is possible to weave or not. COVER FACTOR CALCULATOR Estimates the weight of the cloth roller as well of the length of fabric on it. FABRIC LENGTH & WEIGHT CALCULATOR Calculates the remaining length and weight of yarn on the warp beam. REMAINING WARP BEAM LENGTH & WEIGHT CALCULATOR Converts different yarns to their equivalents in other counts. YARN COUNT CONVERTOR PICANOL TEX-APP
